  <h1 id="front-end">Front end developer (mid/senior)</h1>

  <hr class="hr-gradient hr-gradient--tiny hr-gradient--left">

  <h2>About you</h2>
  <p>You're a true professional who loves what you're doing.</p>
  <p>You have a chronic thirst for knowledge and want to be a leading force in your field.</p>
  <p>You realize that you have super powers and want to use them together with us for a better world.</p>
