  <ul>
    <li>Expert knowledge of standards-compliant HTML, CSS (SCSS to be specific) and JavaScript</li>
    <li>Responsive (RWD) techniques and methods</li>
    <li>Device and browser quality assurance, testing and debugging</li>
    <li>Front end performance optimization</li>
    <li>Experience of open source frameworks like Neat, Susy, Ember, jQuery, Zurb Foundation</li>
    <li>Comfortable working with Git</li>
    <li>Basic understanding of UI and UX principles</li>
    <li>Prototyping and designing in the browser</li>
  </ul>

